et/V%C5%A9-Duy-Thanh/Phong-hoa-tuy%E1%BA%BFt-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-g9XvJYAPxnKR-W05Gx18kQ">Phong hoa tuyết nguyệt - 風花雪月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Duy-Thanh/author-A9pMhvZCoNymUTr2lyycBA">Vũ Duy Thanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%A1-ho%C3%A0n-s%C6%A1n-h%E1%BA%ADu-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-V9vVKjOpKm3I_-t-Nl65xw">Tá hoàn sơn hậu ký kỳ 2 - 佐還山後寄其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/T%E1%BA%A7m-L%E1%BB%A5c-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ti%E1%BB%87m-b%E1%BA%A5t-ng%E1%BB%99/poem-YMmFxA6XNoQAK9AbWA6JAA">Tầm Lục Hồng Tiệm bất ngộ - 尋陸鴻漸不遇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-6qD3j1-dnI_XosAv5YFM5Q">Hạo Nhiên thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/Tri%C3%AAu-trung-th%E1%BB%91-%C4%90%C4%83ng-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-b%E1%BA%AFc-cao-phong-t%C3%A1c/poem-IlsndHbPXKYwQbs6bRPcjQ">Triêu trung thố - Đăng Tây Hồ bắc cao phong tác - 朝中措－登西湖北高峰作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/author-nzYvzfRmo_6cp61oWHXvHg">Chu Tử Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tr%C3%B9ng-d%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ph%C3%BA-b%E1%BA%A1ch-c%C3%BAc/poem-MeqYUB_JEXeRYS73_xGImQ">Trùng dương tịch thượng phú bạch cúc - 重陽蓆上賦白菊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
